headline: Trump wants private assets in 401(k)s. How do everyday investors value them?
summary: Private assets might soon be on the menu for your workplace retirement plan. But remember: These investments don’t come with a price tag you can check every day.

headline: Harvard pours $117m into Bitcoin ETF, topping its stakes in Google and Nvidia
summary: Harvard bought $116.7m in BlackRock’s iShares Bitcoin Trust in Q2. Brown University nearly doubled its IBIT stake to over $13 million.
